                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <i>Enhydris</i> is New Latin, from Greek <i>ενυδρις</i> (en-hudris), an otter;
                    <i>plumbea</i> means "plumbeous" (lead-colored).
                    The Chinese name <span lang="zh-TW">鉛色水蛇</span> (qian1se4shui3she2) means "Lead-colored (<span lang="zh-TW">鉛色</span>) water snake (<span lang="zh-TW">水蛇</span>)".
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="species-info-box">
